I - Get opam:
=============

Cf. https://opam.ocaml.org/doc/Install.html

II - Install OCaml via opam:
============================

opam init
opam update
opam switch 4.05.0
eval `opam config env`

III - Get the source and install all dependencies:
==================================================

git clone https://github.com/UnixJunkie/consent.git
cd consent
opam pin add consent $PWD

IV - Compile:
=============

make
